item.title: CVE-2021-36338|2024-08-04T00:54:51.435Z -- dell -- unisphere%20for%20powermax
item.description: Unisphere for PowerMax versions prior to 9.2.2.2 contains a privilege escalation vulnerability. An adjacent malicious user could potentially exploit this vulnerability to escalate their privileges and access functionalities they do not have access to. CVE-2022-31233 addresses the partial fix in CVE-2021-36338.
